<div class="content">
  <h2>Settings</h2>
  <p>
    Here you can change the page settings. Therefore, cookies are used.
    <b>Actually, you have to reload the page after changing the settings to recognize any difference.</b>
    By changing an option <b>you agree with the usage of cookies</b> on this page.
    You can change your opinion at any time by clicking on Reset-button below.
    By doing so, all set cookies from this page are deleted.
  </p>

  <label class="input" for="let-it-snow">
    <span>Let it snow!</span>
  </label>

  {{input class="input-text" type="checkbox" id="let-it-snow" checked=isSnowing change=(action "changeSnowState")
          tabindex=-1}}
  <br>
  <br>
  {{bs-button id="reset" defaultText="Reset" type="primary" buttonType="button" onClick=(action "reset")}}
</div>